'''Amapingu y’urukundo''' ni filimi ikoranye ubuhanga kandi igaragaza ko filimi nyarwanda zimaze gutera intambwe, iyi film igaragaza inkuru y’urukundo ndetse n’ubuhemu, abakinnyi b’ibanze bayo ni Mucyo Willy Audace (wakinnye yitwa Wilson), Shadia Saidi (Jovia), Bertrand Niwemugabo (Trésor) na Agahozo Assouma (Neilla).

Amapingu y’Urukundo imara iminota 144, yakinwe n’anakinnyi bagera kuri 78, amashusho yayo yafatiwe I [[Kigali]], [[Rubavu]] ndetse n’I [[Bujumbura]] mu gihugu cy’u [[Burundi]] mu gihe kingana n’amezi umunani; ni film igaragaramo ubuhanga bw’abakinnyi, amashusho akeye ndetse na tekinike zo gufata amashusho zo mu rwego rushimishije.

Ubwo iyi filimi yerekanwaga, abari babyitabiriye bataramiwe n’itsinda 'A Crew' ririmba injyana ya Hip Hop ari naryo ryahimbye indirimbo (soundtrack) y’iyi filimi. Hari kandi n’ ababyinnyi bashimishije benshi, bazwi ku izina rya Super Steppers.

Filimi yiswe “Amapingu y’urukundo” ni film igaragaza ishusho nyayo y’ubuzima butandukanye bwa sosiyete nyarwanda, yagiye irangwamo amacakubiri n’ihezwa rishingiye ku moko, ubusumbane mu bukungu, ibitsina, uturere n’bindi.

